<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="adba76106a999409361bedb4">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=cc7dc803&authorId=f5a54d49933710bdb8ec5421&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/37d12f2eb9389b50aef14d708e35e5dde7116e82.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>狐狸晨曦</strong>
<span>历史/影视知名撰稿人</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=adba76106a999409361bedb4&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b3fb43166d224f4a3b4b567807f790529922d18e.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
金庸小说中的真实武术，从张三丰创造太极拳说起
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=adba76106a999409361bedb4&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
明末的陈王廷集长拳大洪拳红拳等技法，以张三丰的内家拳理引导，创立了太极拳的固定拳法套路，也就是所谓“陈式太极拳”，奉张三丰为祖师。因此，金庸小说《倚天屠龙记》中，张三丰创立太极拳的说法，并非作家虚构，而是对真实历史的演绎。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-04-16</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">560</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="eba29de2a63a9dc00314e054">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=606d1a25&authorId=caaff993af470388ab739420&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/a2cc7cd98d1001e9547b23cab40e7bec55e797ab.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>冷兵器研究所</strong>
<span>冷兵器第一自媒体，十八般兵器，样样精通</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=eba29de2a63a9dc00314e054&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b21c8701a18b87d607b276840a0828381e30fdbd.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
太极拳就算不能打也能养生？不谈强度的健身指导都是耍流氓
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=eba29de2a63a9dc00314e054&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
一直有个说法，“太极养生，泰拳折寿”。毕竟公园里的老人们们练的都是太极拳，没听说有六七十岁练泰拳养生的。但是这里面还有一些误区，因为养生还是折寿的关键，关键在于训练强度和受重击次数，而不是运动项目。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-12-29</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">296</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="d0746a7defcce5e327263262">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=5631369c&authorId=b3e54008a24ed52773648f25&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/08f790529822720e58ce082377cb0a46f31fabe3.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>历史大学堂</strong>
<span>品读书史，历史堂原创出品</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=d0746a7defcce5e327263262&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/0bd162d9f2d3572ceff9b7378113632763d0c3c6.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
太极拳除了强身健体外, 究竟能不能适应真正的实战搏斗呢
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=d0746a7defcce5e327263262&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
太极拳可以归属为中国古代武术的一种，到了今天已经传承了几百年，并且被归类为内家拳。而这个名字是明朝万历年间武术家王宗岳著书以后才确定了太极拳的。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-01-07</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">224</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="300006d98e9f456e083d53ea">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=150736a3&authorId=d986c0a0c04379765d687821&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d439b6003af33a876e6dfd81c85c10385343b52d.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>在下刀掌门</strong>
<span>历史评论学者社群</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=300006d98e9f456e083d53ea&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/3b292df5e0fe9925110e82e33aa85edf8db17107.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
历史上有两个“张三丰”，但太极拳与他俩根本没有一毛钱关系
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=300006d98e9f456e083d53ea&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">

张三丰，道家武当派开山鼻祖，在金庸的武侠小说《倚天屠龙记》中给人印象最深刻的就是张三丰在少林寺习武的桥段。清代儒学家朱仕丰曾经评价张三丰说：古今练道者无数，而得天地之造化者，张三丰也！...</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-05-13</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">195</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="632fc520d0d1e1e216bfbb24">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=dcd9c8ac&authorId=0c64d05c8ae6314118d96e27&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/0bd162d9f2d3572c578571968313632762d0c311.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>头条说</strong>
<span>关注热点，解读背后的知识</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=632fc520d0d1e1e216bfbb24&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/aec379310a55b3199ef1cb5a49a98226cffc1790.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
徐晓冬秒杀的是不是假太极？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=632fc520d0d1e1e216bfbb24&lemmaId=84009&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
借太极拳师雷雷被格斗教练徐晓冬秒杀的热闹，把我11年前了解到的太极拳在湖南的一些旧事给翻出来，或许有人会喜欢看。

11年前，也即我做记者的元年。我进入潇湘晨报当时的“特色周末”栏目做的第一个系列，是“潇湘侠影”，多谢当时的领导，竟然允许我做这么个非主流的选题。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-05-03</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">180</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
